01:17:43.997 --> 01:17:45.373
Crush his face!

700
01:17:50.003 --> 01:17:51.463
- Do it!
- Take him out!

701
01:17:51.629 --> 01:17:53.298
Drop it! Drop it!

702
01:18:16.112 --> 01:18:17.530
God.

703
01:18:37.550 --> 01:18:39.302
Linen run!

704
01:18:39.511 --> 01:18:43.264
Get a move on.
I'm trying to make a living here.

705
01:18:45.058 --> 01:18:49.104
Frank. my man. Florence Nightingale.

706
01:18:49.896 --> 01:18:52.649
- How you feeling?
- All right.

707
01:18:52.816 --> 01:18:57.237
- Three weeks and you're out. man.
- Feels like three years.

708
01:18:57.445 --> 01:19:01.074
Come on. man.
Three weeks is a blink.

709
01:19:02.742 --> 01:19:05.412
What'd they do with the kid?

710
01:19:08.289 --> 01:19:12.377
They sent him home. man.
What'd you think? You know.

711
01:19:14.421 --> 01:19:18.383
You know. the kid told me once...

712
01:19:19.426 --> 01:19:25.223
..."Your body has to be in prison. but
your mind can be wherever it wants."

713
01:19:25.890 --> 01:19:27.851
He tell you that?

714
01:19:31.813 --> 01:19:34.899
Listen. I brought you
some toilet paper...

715
01:19:35.066 --> 01:19:39.654
...in case. you know. you want
to write some poetry or something.

716
01:19:41.573 --> 01:19:45.869
Hey. Colonel Klink.
Let me out of here. man.

717
01:19:50.415 --> 01:19:53.376
Frank. man.
it wasn't your fault. okay?

718
01:19:53.752 --> 01:19:55.879
Remember that.

719
01:20:04.387 --> 01:20:09.559
Roberta. have Miss Lowell photographed
for an I.D. For visitation.

720
01:20:09.726 --> 01:20:12.645
I'm reinstating
Mr. Leone's privileges.

721
01:20:12.812 --> 01:20:14.147
Yes. sir.

722
01:20:14.356 --> 01:20:19.611
- I want to make sure Frank's all right.
- He's fine. He's recovering.

723
01:20:19.778 --> 01:20:24.574
In three weeks he'll be out. and you can
look forward to a happy life together.

724
01:20:24.783 --> 01:20:28.286
- Thank you for coming.
- Thank you. warden.

725
01:20:34.209 --> 01:20:36.586
Okay. look into the light.

726
01:20:45.762 --> 01:20:47.847
- Hi. baby.
- Hi.

727
01:20:48.014 --> 01:20:51.851
Hi. come here. you.

728
01:20:52.560 --> 01:20:55.271
- I was so worried.
- You look great.

729
01:20:55.480 --> 01:21:00.360
Thirty-minute visit. Leone. Compliments
of the warden. Don't waste it.

730
01:21:00.527 --> 01:21:04.072
- How do you feel?
- Good. thanks. sweetheart.

731
01:21:04.280 --> 01:21:09.786
Thirty minutes. You need any help.
just give us a call. huh?

732
01:21:13.957 --> 01:21:17.919
- Are they all like that?
- Don't worry. You look great.

733
01:21:18.086 --> 01:21:19.421
You look...

734
01:21:19.629 --> 01:21:23.216
Don't tell me what I look like.
I can't stand it.

735
01:21:23.383 --> 01:21:26.553
I've missed you so much.

736
01:21:35.353 --> 01:21:39.274
No more separations. Promise?

737
01:21:39.482 --> 01:21:42.235
I promise.

738
01:21:59.627 --> 01:22:02.088
- Time's up.
- Nice view.

739
01:22:02.297 --> 01:22:05.091
- What's the matter with you?
- Time's up.

740
01:22:05.258 --> 01:22:08.720
- The warden said half an hour.
- He changed his mind.

741
01:22:09.929 --> 01:22:12.932
What do you mean?
I wanna talk to the warden.

742
01:22:13.183 --> 01:22:18.104
What you wanna do is keep your mouth
shut. fix your clothes and get out.

743
01:22:18.313 --> 01:22:21.024
- Come on.
- Don't touch her.

744
01:22:21.775 --> 01:22:24.194
What did you say?

745
01:22:24.361 --> 01:22:29.407
- Don't touch her? You don't learn. pal.
- Hey. I'm leaving.

746
01:22:33.953 --> 01:22:37.665
Three weeks.
Three weeks. Three weeks.

747
01:23:06.194 --> 01:23:08.113
Leone.

748
01:23:08.571 --> 01:23:10.699
Come here.

749
01:23:16.663 --> 01:23:17.956
Do I know you?

750
01:23:18.164 --> 01:23:21.835
No. you don't know me. Frank.
but I know you.

751
01:23:22.127 --> 01:23:24.671
I was at Treadmore with you.

752
01:23:26.798 --> 01:23:28.967
A-block.

753
01:23:29.759 --> 01:23:33.430
- Treadmore don't have an A-block.
- That's right.

754
01:23:33.596 --> 01:23:37.559
- We got something else in common.
- Yeah. what's that?

755
01:23:37.767 --> 01:23:39.519
We're both getting out soon.

756
01:23:39.811 --> 01:23:44.607
You in a few weeks.
Me. I'm gone the day after tomorrow.

757
01:23:45.400 --> 01:23:47.444
What happened to you?

758
01:23:47.694 --> 01:23:50.613
One beating too many.

759
01:23:50.822 --> 01:23:55.952
I served some hard time in this place.
We both have. am I right?

760
01:23:57.454 --> 01:24:00.874
Yeah. you're right about that.

761
01:24:01.124 --> 01:24:05.503
You need anything when I get out?
Can I get you anything?

762
01:24:05.795 --> 01:24:10.717
- No. I'm all right. Thanks.
- I'm just lucky. I guess.

763
01:24:10.884 --> 01:24:17.098
I got a job lined up. Temporary. but
it pays a grand for two hours of work.

764
01:24:17.390 --> 01:24:20.602
- That's not bad. is it?
- What do you gotta do?

765
01:24:24.314 --> 01:24:29.444
I just gotta rape this bitch. I get an
extra hundred every time she screams.

766
01:24:29.652 --> 01:24:33.406
- I'll kill you for that!
- Payback time. Frank.

767
01:24:33.656 --> 01:24:35.742
- Chink says hello.
- You touch her. you're dead!

768
01:24:36.201 --> 01:24:39.037
Hey. bailiff! Guard!
Guard! Somebody!

769
01:24:39.204 --> 01:24:43.708
Manly! Manly! Guard!

770
01:24:44.292 --> 01:24:46.878
- What's your problem?
- I gotta use the phone.

771
01:24:47.087 --> 01:24:52.342
- You know your privileges. No phone.
- That guy is gonna kill my girlfriend.

772
01:24:52.592 --> 01:24:55.095
- What guy?
- The guy that was just here.

773
01:24:55.261 --> 01:25:00.100
- The guy in the wheelchair!
- What are you trying to pull. Leone?

774
01:25:00.266 --> 01:25:03.895
Don't play with me. Manly.
Please. I gotta warn her.

775
01:25:04.104 --> 01:25:08.274
Everybody's got problems. Leone.
Get some sleep.

776
01:25:08.441 --> 01:25:13.655
Goddamn. you fat motherfucker!
Goddamn!

777
01:25:18.451 --> 01:25:23.581
Hey. Frank. Doing some
spring-cleaning. huh. man?

778
01:25:24.207 --> 01:25:26.918
Dallas. come here.

779
01:25:27.168 --> 01:25:29.004
Yeah?

780
01:25:32.132 --> 01:25:36.219
- What is it. man?
- I need some help.

781
01:25:36.386 --> 01:25:39.014
No questions asked.

782
01:25:41.016 --> 01:25:44.936
You're busting out?
You got less than three weeks.

783
01:25:45.103 --> 01:25:46.396
Just help me.

784
01:25:46.646 --> 01:25:49.983
- This is gonna take days.
- I need it tonight.

785
01:25:50.191 --> 01:25:53.820
I can't do that.
Everything is gonna be locked up.

786
01:25:54.029 --> 01:25:57.574
There's a con getting
out of here tomorrow.

787
01:25:57.824 --> 01:26:01.453
- Chink Weber paid him to get Melissa.
- I understand.

788
01:26:01.745 --> 01:26:07.250
I'd love to help. but I can't do
the impossible. You're hurting my arm.

789
01:26:13.340 --> 01:26:16.217
I'll take you with me.

790
01:26:18.345 --> 01:26:20.972
No shit?

791
01:26:21.514 --> 01:26:24.267
- What's the plan?
- You'll know when you gotta know.

792
01:26:26.269 --> 01:26:29.773
Going for the tunnels. huh. man?

793
01:26:29.981 --> 01:26:32.442
You just be here. all right?

794
01:26:33.651 --> 01:26:36.112
Convict. move it out of there!

795
01:26:36.279 --> 01:26:41.326
Hey. use some bleach on that. Frank.
I'm coming out. Colonel Klink.

796
01:26:45.622 --> 01:26:46.915
Linen run.

797
01:26:47.123 --> 01:26:50.585
- Evening. Officer Vazquez.
- You're late. Get in there.

798
01:26:50.835 --> 01:26:52.128
- Yes. sir.
- Quick.

799
01:26:52.379 --> 01:26:55.590
- I'll be real quick.
- Still making that jailhouse booze?

800
01:26:55.882 --> 01:27:00.387
Absolutely not. sir. I'm on the wagon.
I joined Alcoholics Unanimous.

801
01:27:00.637 --> 01:27:03.640
- You got some line of shit.
- It's bad on my nervous system.

802
01:27:03.890 --> 01:27:06.643
- Makes me talk too much.
- Just make it quick.

803
01:27:06.893 --> 01:27:10.355
Yeah. I'll be right out. sir.
Right out.

804
01:27:18.238 --> 01:27:20.782
No. Help! Oh. shit!

805
01:27:23.243 --> 01:27:25.328
Help me!

806
01:27:27.539 --> 01:27:29.290
Come on. Frank. Let's go.

807
01:27:29.541 --> 01:27:31.876
Okay. come on. That's it.

808
01:27:35.422 --> 01:27:38.883
- All right. we got 10 minutes. Move it.
- All right.

809
01:27:39.134 --> 01:27:41.094
Sweet dreams. Moby Dick.

810
01:27:41.845 --> 01:27:43.430
- Frank?
- Come on.

811
01:27:43.722 --> 01:27:45.598
The tools. man.

812
01:28:00.238 --> 01:28:01.656
You got it.

813
01:28:03.950 --> 01:28:06.453
Okay. here I go.

814
01:28:07.412 --> 01:28:09.706
Oh. God. I'm jumping.

815
01:28:12.751 --> 01:28:15.378
Man. there's rats in here.

816
01:28:27.182 --> 01:28:29.809
- All right. I'm all right. No!
- What?

817
01:28:29.976 --> 01:28:33.396
- This way. It's a shortcut to the plant.
- It's this way.

818
01:28:33.605 --> 01:28:39.069
No. man. I remember the map.
It's this way. I'm positive. Let's go!

819
01:28:57.879 --> 01:28:59.631
D.T.A.. Frank.

820
01:29:01.716 --> 01:29:05.178
Ain't that what you taught me. man?
D.T.A.

821
01:29:05.345 --> 01:29:07.972
Right on schedule. Frank.

822
01:29:08.181 --> 01:29:10.892
I'm sorry. man.
You were my ticket out of here.

823
01:29:11.476 --> 01:29:13.561
Damn you!

824
01:29:17.607 --> 01:29:22.195
You had me set up the whole time?!

825
01:29:22.404 --> 01:29:27.659
Not the whole time. I got
30 years to go. man. Thirty years.

826
01:29:28.702 --> 01:29:31.454
The warden made me a deal.

827
01:29:32.872 --> 01:29:34.958
Dumb bastard!

828
01:29:35.208 --> 01:29:37.335
They made me a deal. man!
A deal!

829
01:29:37.544 --> 01:29:41.006
We don't make deals
with escaping prisoners.

830
01:29:44.092 --> 01:29:46.720
What the hell are you talking about?

831
01:29:46.970 --> 01:29:49.556
- You said if I delivered...
- Shut up.

832
01:29:49.848 --> 01:29:53.476
- You're going back to the population.
- Population?

833
01:29:53.685 --> 01:29:57.147
You can't do this to me. warden.
You can't do this.

834
01:29:57.397 --> 01:30:00.650
I snitched him off.
They're gonna kill me. I'm finished.

835
01:30:00.817 --> 01:30:02.777
Tough.

836
01:30:03.153 --> 01:30:07.115
Look. I came through. goddamn it!
We had a deal!

837
01:30:09.576 --> 01:30:12.328
That's enough.
You're gonna kill him.

838
01:30:13.955 --> 01:30:15.165
That's enough.

839
01:30:22.005 --> 01:30:24.966
This is an automatic 10 years. Frank.

840
01:30:25.175 --> 01:30:28.803
It's 10 years for a second
escape attempt.

841
01:30:28.970 --> 01:30:32.807
I knew you'd cross the line. I told
them you were a hard-core criminal.

842
01:30:33.016 --> 01:30:37.395
They'll believe me now.
And you better believe me.

843
01:30:37.604 --> 01:30:41.316
You better believe that you'll
be doing hard time here...

844
01:30:41.566 --> 01:30:44.110
...for the rest of your life.

845
01:30:45.487 --> 01:30:47.781
Manly. you know what to do.

846
01:31:01.586 --> 01:31:03.630
Some dealmaker.

847
01:31:13.014 --> 01:31:14.349
See...

848
01:31:14.641 --> 01:31:17.185
...shit does float. doesn't it?

849
01:31:17.477 --> 01:31:19.396
Hey. you know what else?

850
01:31:19.562 --> 01:31:23.942
You don't have to worry about
that psycho hurting your girlfriend.

851
01:31:24.192 --> 01:31:27.779
We decided to keep him in here.
Didn't we. officer?

852
01:31:35.954 --> 01:31:37.997
She's not my type.

853
01:31:42.002 --> 01:31:42.085
We'll teach him a lesson.
We'll graduate you with honours.

854
01:31:42.085 --> 01:31:45.005
We'll teach him a lesson.
We'll graduate you with honours.

855
01:31:45.255 --> 01:31:49.843
Turn on the steam.
Turn on the fucking steam!

856
01:31:50.051 --> 01:31:51.678
Put him in it.

857
01:31:52.012 --> 01:31:53.888
Get him in there.

858
01:32:00.145 --> 01:32:03.023
Bring him in here! Come on!

859
01:32:09.029 --> 01:32:11.114
Come on!

860
01:32:20.123 --> 01:32:22.167
Rape this.

861
01:32:24.836 --> 01:32:29.883
My face! My face is burning!
My face!

862
01:32:46.191 --> 01:32:48.026
I'll kill you!

863
01:33:14.886 --> 01:33:16.971
School's out. punk.

864
01:34:18.158 --> 01:34:19.826
Frank.

865
01:34:21.953 --> 01:34:24.664
Frank. don't leave me here. man.

866
01:34:33.381 --> 01:34:35.258
I'm sorry.

867
01:34:36.009 --> 01:34:38.094
Take me with you.

868
01:34:59.491 --> 01:35:01.785
Let him go. Manly.

869
01:35:02.077 --> 01:35:03.953
Let him go.

870
01:35:12.629 --> 01:35:14.839
What are you gonna do with that?

871
01:35:15.131 --> 01:35:16.883
You okay. Frank?

872
01:35:17.467 --> 01:35:19.386
I'm okay. Dallas.

873
01:35:20.303 --> 01:35:23.556
You can trust me. Frank.
You can trust me.

874
01:35:23.848 --> 01:35:27.018
- Put it down. Dallas.
- Put it down.

875
01:35:27.310 --> 01:35:31.147
- I won't hurt you anymore.
- Oh. yeah?

876
01:35:33.316 --> 01:35:37.362
- You don't wanna do it.
- You fat piece of shit.

877
01:35:37.529 --> 01:35:38.988
Don't do it. Dallas.

878
01:35:39.572 --> 01:35:43.326
- What. are you trying to scare me?
- Dallas. don't.

879
01:35:45.078 --> 01:35:48.081
- You won't do it.
- Oh. yeah?

880
01:35:48.415 --> 01:35:52.627
- You don't got the balls to do it. punk.
- You're wrong.

881
01:35:52.836 --> 01:35:55.380
- Stoolie.
- You're wrong.

882
01:35:56.339 --> 01:35:58.508
- Put it down.
- You're wrong!

883
01:35:58.800 --> 01:36:00.260
No!

884
01:36:19.404 --> 01:36:23.450
Switch to backup. Sir. we've got
a power outage in C-wing.

885
01:36:24.200 --> 01:36:26.745
Get some men to that utility quarter.

886
01:36:51.478 --> 01:36:55.774
You better have a good reason for not
telling me you knew Leone was escaping.

887
01:36:55.982 --> 01:36:58.818
I've got a dead officer and
a dead inmate.

888
01:36:59.069 --> 01:37:01.363
And I don't have any answers.
Do you?

889
01:37:01.529 --> 01:37:05.200
I was trying to save an informant's
life by keeping it secret.

890
01:37:05.408 --> 01:37:10.038
Why would a man who's got
three weeks to go try to break out?

891
01:37:10.372 --> 01:37:13.083
We can ask him
when we catch him.

892
01:37:33.978 --> 01:37:38.233
Busted cable. utility corridor.
He's going to the roof.

893
01:39:13.411 --> 01:39:15.538
Bring up zone two.

894
01:39:16.414 --> 01:39:18.375
Can't you get any more light in there?

895
01:39:18.583 --> 01:39:20.043
Captain Meissner.

896
01:39:20.210 --> 01:39:22.504
This is Osner.
I'm in the well room.

897
01:39:22.629 --> 01:39:24.881
Looks like this is where he went out.

898
01:39:36.184 --> 01:39:39.437
Sir. that has got to be at least
200 yards underwater.

899
01:39:39.646 --> 01:39:42.899
- Do you really think he made it?
- Maybe not. Mr. Braden.

900
01:39:43.233 --> 01:39:45.819
But until you bring me a body.
I've got an escaped prisoner.

901
01:39:46.027 --> 01:39:49.155
- This is Drumgoole. I want sector four.
- Meissner. sector four.

902
01:39:49.322 --> 01:39:52.701
- What do you have?
- Right now. nothing. sir.

903
01:39:52.951 --> 01:39:56.454
I'm thinking of calling in the
local and state police.

904
01:39:56.746 --> 01:40:01.626
No! No outside agencies.
I repeat. no outside agencies.

905
01:40:01.835 --> 01:40:05.588
This is an internal matter.
He's alive. I want him.

906
01:40:05.839 --> 01:40:10.135
- Arm a tactical squad and meet me.
- Yes. sir.

907
01:40:11.094 --> 01:40:15.306
Mr. Braden. you will
continue this search.

908
01:40:38.913 --> 01:40:41.416
You won't get away with it.

909
01:40:42.959 --> 01:40:44.878
You know that. don't you?

910
01:40:46.296 --> 01:40:48.631
I could've got out.

911
01:40:50.633 --> 01:40:54.054
But I'm not going to spend my life...

912
01:40:54.346 --> 01:40:58.099
...running from you.

913
01:41:02.645 --> 01:41:04.689
Paul. look at this.

914
01:41:08.026 --> 01:41:09.736
Get your ass inside.

915
01:41:10.028 --> 01:41:12.072
Whoa. hold it.

916
01:41:12.822 --> 01:41:16.076
- You can't use me as a hostage...
- Shut up! Shut up!

917
01:41:16.326 --> 01:41:19.287
You recognize that chair?

918
01:41:19.579 --> 01:41:24.042
You built it. didn't you?
Now get in there. Get in there!

919
01:41:24.292 --> 01:41:26.628
Don't even think about moving.

920
01:41:29.756 --> 01:41:34.260
You think you're gonna take me
to hell. huh? I'll show you hell!

921
01:41:36.012 --> 01:41:38.598
All right. over there.

922
01:41:39.140 --> 01:41:41.017
Move your leg!

923
01:41:41.351 --> 01:41:45.814
Dallas. he fried.
the way you're gonna fry.

924
01:41:47.315 --> 01:41:52.737
First Base. you took him downstairs.
you broke his goddamn neck!

925
01:41:55.407 --> 01:42:00.620
I'm gonna fry your brains.
What do you know? It's a perfect fit.

926
01:42:01.538 --> 01:42:03.623
Move! Move!

927
01:42:05.166 --> 01:42:09.796
You can't make this work.
You're not smart enough. You're stupid.

928
01:42:09.963 --> 01:42:11.464
You're scum.

929
01:42:11.631 --> 01:42:14.718
Shut up! I'll show you scum.

930
01:42:16.011 --> 01:42:19.931
You can't kill a man. You're not
a murderer. You don't have the guts.

931
01:42:26.104 --> 01:42:29.065
Ten more years.
Isn't that what you said?

932
01:42:30.025 --> 01:42:31.860
How about 20?

933
01:42:32.360 --> 01:42:33.862
How about 30?

934
01:42:34.154 --> 01:42:38.825
No. it doesn't matter what they give
me because you won't be satisfied...

935
01:42:39.117 --> 01:42:40.535
...till you got me for life.

936
01:42:40.702 --> 01:42:42.787
Make a hole.

937
01:42:43.079 --> 01:42:44.706
Take it down!

938
01:42:47.167 --> 01:42:49.461
I ain't doing life for nothing.

939
01:42:50.795 --> 01:42:53.131
Come on. Lean on it. man!

940
01:42:53.340 --> 01:42:56.301
They're gonna break that door down.

941
01:42:56.551 --> 01:42:59.512
And they're going to take
your skull apart!

942
01:42:59.721 --> 01:43:02.891
You're going to beg me
to let them kill you.

943
01:43:03.308 --> 01:43:05.810
- Come on. break it down!
- Meissner!

944
01:43:07.354 --> 01:43:09.522
Harder. man. Harder!

945
01:43:13.735 --> 01:43:16.029
Come on. lean on it.

946
01:43:16.529 --> 01:43:18.198
No!

947
01:43:20.116 --> 01:43:21.743
No!

948
01:43:23.953 --> 01:43:25.580
Take out the glass!

949
01:43:28.958 --> 01:43:31.086
Shoot! Shoot me!

950
01:43:31.252 --> 01:43:32.796
- Don't shoot!
- Shoot!

951
01:43:33.004 --> 01:43:35.548
He has his hand taped to the lever.

952
01:43:36.049 --> 01:43:37.550
No!

953
01:43:38.093 --> 01:43:42.305
- Don't shoot!
- Hold your fire. Hold your fire.

954
01:43:42.472 --> 01:43:43.848
Come on. shoot!

955
01:43:46.393 --> 01:43:48.019
Hold your fire!

956
01:43:51.147 --> 01:43:53.858
Relax. Just relax.

957
01:43:54.734 --> 01:43:58.321
Glad you're here. Meissner. This
wouldn't be official without witnesses.

958
01:43:58.488 --> 01:44:03.660
He's bluffing. He's wants me to take
responsibility for his escape attempt.

959
01:44:03.993 --> 01:44:07.872
I don't want a confession.
You set me up. You set everything up!

960
01:44:08.039 --> 01:44:12.585
- I don't know what you're talking about.
- I'm talking about Chink Weber!

961
01:44:12.752 --> 01:44:14.546
The goons.

962
01:44:15.005 --> 01:44:18.008
The cop that was gonna rape Melissa.

963
01:44:18.842 --> 01:44:20.176
Dallas.

964
01:44:21.177 --> 01:44:23.680
The killing of the kid.

965
01:44:24.848 --> 01:44:26.933
Guilty on all counts.

966
01:44:27.100 --> 01:44:32.480
Prove it! That's your problem.
You can't prove anything.

967
01:44:32.689 --> 01:44:37.444
I don't have to prove nothing.
I came here for an execution.

968
01:44:37.610 --> 01:44:41.031
I demand to be released from here!

969
01:44:42.115 --> 01:44:43.616
No!

970
01:44:43.783 --> 01:44:48.455
Don't do it. Leone. Don't do it.
Take it easy.

971
01:44:49.205 --> 01:44:52.625
You deserve payback.

972
01:44:52.876 --> 01:44:54.294
Frank!

973
01:44:56.588 --> 01:44:58.631
Please. Frank.

974
01:44:59.966 --> 01:45:03.887
Don't kill me. It's true.

975
01:45:07.015 --> 01:45:10.643
I confess. Mr. Meissner.

976
01:45:10.935 --> 01:45:13.938
Everything that he said was true.

977
01:45:14.189 --> 01:45:17.150
I set him up. Everything.

978
01:45:21.071 --> 01:45:22.614
Please.

979
01:45:23.990 --> 01:45:26.284
Don't kill me.

980
01:45:27.869 --> 01:45:29.079
Don't...

981
01:45:29.829 --> 01:45:35.502
See you in hell. Drumgoole.

982
01:45:53.103 --> 01:45:55.647
Works better with this.

983
01:45:57.691 --> 01:46:00.151
Take him to the hole. Mr. Meissner.

984
01:46:00.527 --> 01:46:04.781
Mr. Braden. take the prisoner
to the hole.

985
01:46:05.073 --> 01:46:06.991
- Cuff him.
- Yes. sir.

986
01:46:07.283 --> 01:46:11.705
Somebody get me
out of this chair.

987
01:46:13.289 --> 01:46:14.791
Come on.

988
01:46:19.421 --> 01:46:24.217
Thank you. Mr. Meissner.
I said take him to the hole.

989
01:46:24.384 --> 01:46:26.302
I can't do that.

990
01:46:27.053 --> 01:46:28.888
Take the warden into custody.

991
01:46:29.139 --> 01:46:32.350
- I said take him. What are you doing?
- Cuff him.

992
01:46:32.642 --> 01:46:38.273
Stop it! I am warden of this institution.
and you will obey... Stop that!

993
01:46:38.732 --> 01:46:44.237
That was just a stupid confession to
try and save my life. Are you crazy?

994
01:46:44.654 --> 01:46:46.990
No. but you are.

995
01:46:47.240 --> 01:46:52.579
Until this matter's resolved in a judicial
inquiry. you'll remain in our custody.

996
01:46:55.040 --> 01:46:57.834
I'll have your ass for this.

997
01:46:58.084 --> 01:47:01.755
I'll have your ass.

998
01:47:02.839 --> 01:47:04.591
Move him!

999
01:47:16.478 --> 01:47:19.189
I only wanted to do my time. captain.

1000
01:47:19.689 --> 01:47:22.275
You'll get your chance.

1001
01:47:22.442 --> 01:47:24.652
Move him.

1002
01:47:45.298 --> 01:47:47.509
Hey. Ernie.

1003
01:47:47.676 --> 01:47:49.636
Hang in there. Frank.

1004
01:47:50.011 --> 01:47:51.554
Hey. Frank?

1005
01:47:51.763 --> 01:47:53.807
- Eclipse.
- Take care.

1006
01:47:54.015 --> 01:47:56.768
You too. Thanks a lot. big man.

1007
01:47:56.935 --> 01:48:00.271
Yeah. That okay?

1008
01:48:00.438 --> 01:48:02.273
It's all right.

1009
01:48:04.776 --> 01:48:09.781
Got this one from
Fidel Castro himself.

1010
01:48:12.075 --> 01:48:14.828
- See you. big man.
- Okay.

1011
01:48:35.724 --> 01:48:37.726
Hold it.

1012
01:48:38.018 --> 01:48:40.979
Crack the outside!

1013
01:48:41.896 --> 01:48:45.942
- Know what I'll miss most about you?
- What's that?

1014
01:48:46.818 --> 01:48:49.696
Your incredible smile.

1015
01:49:01.583 --> 01:49:05.628
- Take care of yourself. Leone.
- Thanks. captain.

1016
01:49:17.474 --> 01:49:18.683
Lock 'em!
